WEBVTT

00:03:54.159 --> 00:04:00.560
either through revolution,
higher taxes, or wars.

00:04:00.560 --> 00:04:02.889
None of those are on my bucket list.

00:04:02.889 --> 00:04:04.025
(Laughter)

00:04:04.025 --> 00:04:06.086
Now, there's another way to do it,

00:04:06.086 --> 00:04:10.226
and that's by increasing justness
in corporate behavior,

00:04:10.226 --> 00:04:12.989
but the way that we're
operating right now,

00:04:12.989 --> 00:04:16.983
that would require
a tremendous change in behavior,

00:04:16.983 --> 00:04:20.930
and like an addict trying to kick a habit,

00:04:20.930 --> 00:04:24.436
the first step is to acknowledge
that you have a problem.

00:04:24.436 --> 00:04:28.337
And let me just say,
this profits mania that we're on

00:04:28.337 --> 00:04:30.636
is so deeply entrenched